          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37870782/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37870782/" class="">第51页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1274910/" class=" " title="万火归一">万火归一</a>
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="37870782">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">萧伯纳说：一切高技能的专业都是针对门外汉的密谋。我还要再向前迈一步：在技术垄断文化里，一切专家都被赋予了神父样的魅力。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-05-29 16:01</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                萧伯纳说：一切高技能的专业都是针对门外汉的密谋。我还要再向前迈一步：在技术垄断文化里，一切专家都被赋予了神父样的魅力。
